Module com.cateringfx
Package com.cateringfx.model

Class MenuElement

java.lang.Object
com.cateringfx.model.MenuElement
Direct Known Subclasses:
Aliment, Dish
public abstract class MenuElement extends Object

Abstract class to define a basic elements needed to represent a food Menu by its name, description and abstract methods: getCalories(), getCarbohydrates(), getFat(), isMilk(), isNuts(), isEgg() and isGluten() to be implemented by its subclasses.

Version:
1.0.
Author:
Francisco David Manzanedo Valle.
